RawLine: SDM_1104101525,我也聽說洛雁谷底天仙環繞，收藏著靈丹妙藥和絕世武功，只要擊敗谷主，一切便盡歸你手。,我也听说洛雁谷底天仙环绕，收藏着灵丹妙药和绝世武功，只要击败谷主，一切便尽归你手。

Items.mt: I also heard that the bottom of Luo Yan Valley is surrounded by celestial immortals, where there are magic pills and excellent martial arts, and if you defeat the valley master, everything will be in your hands.
